tool_description: The Bitrate Calculator is the API that will help you in promoting high quality for your internet Video Streams.
name: Bitrate Calculator
title: Bitrate Calculator

api_list.name: Quality  to 1600x900 - [Video Type 1]
api_list.description:
This call exemplify using the **params list:**

1. **FPS** - Frames Per Second - Using 60
2. **QPP** - Pixel quality percentage - Using 100%
3. **Audio Bitrate** - Audio Quality - Using 192
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://bitrate-calculator.p.rapidapi.com/1600_900/60/100/192"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "bitrate-calculator.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
